                    dates="Oct 2020 - June 2023"
                    location="Remote"
                    accomplishments={[
                        "Develop intelligent software features using network models, density estimation, hypothesis testing, time series models, cluster analysis, linear models, change point detection to provide customers actionable insights for improving digital experience & network performance",
