                        "Recognized as a high potential employee to participate in  360 leadership development program"
                    ]}
                />
                    <WorkItem
                    company="Walmart"
                    jobRole="Staff Data Scientist"
                    jobRole2="Senior Data Scientist"
                    jobRole3="Decision Manager II"
                    jobRole4="2015 Summer Intern"
                    dates="Aug 2016 - Oct 2020"
                    location="Bentonville, AR"
                    accomplishments={[
                        "Boosted online grocery sales by $160 million using Hive to develop an automated weekly audit report for 1 billion store-items that identifies discrepancies among ecommerce site back-end systems to fix items that are erroneously showing as out-of-stock, to provide root cause analysis for back-end system engineers, and to provide leadership with inventory accuracy KPI’s",
